
Overview of noun refrigeration

The noun refrigeration has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                  
1. (2) refrigeration, infrigidation -- (the process of cooling or freezing (e.g., food) for preservative purposes)
2. refrigeration -- (deliberately lowering the body's temperature for therapeutic purposes; "refrigeration by immersing the patient's body in a cold bath")
